  "title": "PROJECT MANAGER (CIVIL)",
  "description": "<h5>Job Description &amp; Requirements</h5>\n<p><strong>Job Responsibilities :</strong></p>\n<p>1. Overall reporting to Project Director.</p>\n<p>2. Responsible for technical and engineering matters.</p>\n<p>3. Involved in project planning, monitoring and scheduling of site activities.</p>\n<p>4. Involved in monthly progress claim and monthly progress reporting.</p>\n<p>5. Ensuring environmental, safety and health aspect on site.</p>\n<p>6. Liaise and coordinate with clients and sub contractors.</p>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements :</strong></p>\n<p>1. Bachelor Degree in Civil &amp; Structural Engineering recognised by PE Board or BCA.</p>\n<p>2. Proficient in Microsoft Office.</p>\n<p>3. Positve working attitude.</p>\n<p>4. Good Interpersonal and analytical skills.</p>",
